HEADWORD: Forming
<hw>Form"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The act or process of
giving form or shape to anything; as, in shipbuilding, the exact shaping
of partially shaped timbers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Formless</ent>⟦br⟧
